{"tid":2137910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張竹君稱整體確診仍很高需再觀望 籲市民要忍耐勿鬆懈","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:19:23.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"45c55fc4ae6b136ea4fbc21c72d6eca026e7388f","tid":2137910,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"張竹君稱整體確診仍很高需再觀望 籲市民要忍耐勿鬆懈<br />\n2020-08-03 HKT 17:15<br />\n<br />\n&quot;本港新增80宗新型肺炎確診個案，是13日以來，單日確診個案首次少於100宗。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，今日的新增確診數字看似較低，但整體仍然很高，回想以往只要出現一、兩宗確診個案已經很緊張。她認為要觀望多幾天，才知趨勢是否向下。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541575-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541575-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=6dccbb46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541575-20200803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5f5df406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541575-20200803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">忍耐勿鬆懈，可以照出街</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}